    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between daily utility and premium comfort. The exterior maintains a strong curb appeal with a vibrant finish, though close inspection reveals minor road-wear such as small stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free; the upholstery is intact with only gentle creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior plastics remain supple and fade-free. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. The engine idles quietly and accelerates smoothly, while the transmission provides crisp, predictable shifts. All onboard electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, are fully operational. With a consistent maintenance history and recent fluid services, this vehicle is turn-key ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
